Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙真的回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子的老師不是和你聯絡過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使她故意說謊也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 喂 內田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 佑那傢伙也在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又有什麼關係 總之遙也回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐看起來回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是內田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是今天的例會怎麼也要出席
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那要現在回東京嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}\N暴 \N風 \N雨 \N的 \N夜 \N晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說是美有樹被告白了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 不對不對 是明日香啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明日香被田中君告白了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 好像有客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可愛的小客人們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了...佑的...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 是大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃點心的話 在平常擺的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑一直受你們照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我們才是 總是添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇 下次再來我家玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要勇一來 家裏就非常熱鬧 阿姨最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹 快點過來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那過會見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 沒有啤酒嗎 啤酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 阿姨怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些醉了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣也不錯啊 很高興的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 遙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是被捲入什麼奇怪的事件裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒...沒什麼事啦 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很讓人擔心啊 到底跑那裏去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又那樣把真相隱瞞起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 後藤剛才在隔壁的房間裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 沒...沒啦 我一直在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的時候 好像看見二樓的窗戶裏好像有什麼人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是後藤君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心...心理作用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二樓除了這間屋子以外 全是空房啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是都做了儲藏室了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個是...幽靈？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午開始說什麼幽靈的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西有被隨便動過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見什麼奇怪的聲音啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你把幽靈趕出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是在身邊帶著這個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不可能帶著這種東西的吧 普通來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡靈 退散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡靈 退散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我吧 快成佛吧 請快成佛吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這樣可糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你藏了什麼吧 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要什麼但是了 快說出來吧 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你們肯定不相信我的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 好友的話 無論說什麼肯定都會相信的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 果然是幽靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事怎麼可能讓人相信！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界裏有未來人 這種話能讓人相信麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這比幽靈的話更不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來來的人什麼的 是幻覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真的在這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不感讓人相信 讓那種傢伙到家裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我來拆穿那個怪物的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊的房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊這傢伙 明明是夏天還穿著黑色的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙怎麼可能是未來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是黑色披風的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都說了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙會被騙我可不會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快點說出真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要來遙這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹...幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的是從未來來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說說15年後會變成怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 快點說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事要怎麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成干擾過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 不破壞時間的約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要對我保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口風緊的我肯定會幫你保密的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住...住手啦 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懲罰...懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 不要鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了 我輸了啦 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君你準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在和大家一起玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓小孩子們隨便玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見啊 美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 下一次你可要來我家玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安定了呢 已經習慣這個時空了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳶 我們還能在這個時空存在多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 現在感覺很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是想著之後的事 也不是辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之後準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明擺著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去消滅龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那傢伙的力量太強大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被送到時空的夾縫中 贏不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓住一直在那傢伙身邊的那個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們在這裏說再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤不要在藤原家待太久了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去借本書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢 我們實在好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 是未來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏著一個穿著怪異服裝的不知所謂的大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能相信那種事 我們真不是普通人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨不像之前那樣囉嗦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那考試不考了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像燕雀說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是...鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很有趣的見面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和那傢伙的過去面對面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好嗎 小子們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人啊 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是有事要找那邊的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰和你這種傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是讓我火大的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我把你那雙眼睛挖出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳶 你這什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的 如果再干涉這個時空的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然時空有不可逆性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但會有什麼影響是無法預測...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:11:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再妨礙我的話 殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說是從小的玩伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你給我消失吧 梟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 逃掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子們 沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個無聊的大叔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要分兩路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟的任務是為確保龍之轉矩的位置進而先攻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦確保了位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩人再一口氣...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉肯定會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉的對手由梟來做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要把龍之轉矩...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗用裝置中出現的異常電磁波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被預測為是由量子共鳴現象產生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經傳送給了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時在當地勘測到的資料製成的量子現象的圖解也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這件事看來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,260)}{\frx-0\fry-8\frz-10}{\bord0\shad1}真無聊~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以推測出在那個區域可能會出現特異的波動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(448,265)}{\frx-0\fry-8\frz-10}{\bord0\shad1}真無聊~\N\N官僚果然都沒有什麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,340)}{\frx-0\fry-8\frz-10}{\bord0\shad1}真無聊~\N\N官僚果然都沒有什麼用啊\N \N\N\N\N\N即使說是精英也都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(468,380)}{\frx-0\fry-8\frz-10}{\bord0\shad1}真無聊~\N\N官僚果然都沒有什麼用啊\N \N\N\N\N\N即使說是精英也都是笨蛋\N \N這裏也都是笨蛋的集合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是個實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我認為把實驗用的地域擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行對波動的位置能進行綜合判斷的調查體式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,250)}{\frx-0\fry-8\frz-8}{\bord0\shad1}特別是精英裏的女人特別囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是唯一能避免被害的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“被害”這個詞我覺得用的不怎麼適當哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田博士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為絕對臨界組織計畫委員會的責任...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員長 我有話說...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 篠原君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府會真的認真考慮量子反應的實用性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣的情況下啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 篠原君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量資料的暫態通信技術的開發 現在整個世界都在做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對的可是世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們卻還在等實驗不一定發生的周邊地區的影響預測報告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不認為效率很糟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 篠原君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險在任何地方都可能發生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才選在離東京很遠的地方做了實驗地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是半官半民的計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要在奇怪的地方擺出官僚作風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是考慮到了地域的安全...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要厚顏無恥了 你這個無用的學者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事前調查什麼的 我來做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裏也培養了很多量子物理學什麼的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是煩的小子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大叔說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肅靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為低氣壓的影響 雄島會有大雨 出門請當心...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雷聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要打到我們家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀盯上了龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果消滅了龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼由於龍之轉矩的不可干涉性 會有發動強大能量的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅會導致這個時空的不安定 整個時空都可能會被消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君有打電話過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是約會的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 真沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 要小心啊 黑披風的那些傢伙又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑披風？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中纜車上襲擊我們的傢伙 還有另一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉 沒想到你會先出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩待會解決也行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從你開始消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有能力阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉 鴉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅秧 時間停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅秧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去搜查 小鷺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時空有難以預測的干涉 要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去捕獲龍之轉矩...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像聽到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是未來的勇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 這是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真火大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完 還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是勇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會把遙交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 遙?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護遙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到這個身體消失為止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的啊 那個人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是勇不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的出現
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切之所以開始都是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有了你...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.70,0:24:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.63,0:24:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏日的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.38,0:24:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田你真的相信有另外一個世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.94,0:24:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.97,0:25:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使分開了也依然是朋友啊 我們
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.49,0:25:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 擦身而過
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.71,0:25:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我力所能及的事嗎


